  <brief_title>The Effect of Emotional Freedom Techniques (EFT) in Smokers Failing a Smoking Cessation Program</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of EFT (Emotional Freedom Techniques) in Smokers Failing a Smoking Cessation Program</official_title>
